      <div class="pw-split__benefit">
        <div class="pw-split__benefit-dot"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
        <span><strong>N-acetyl cysteine</strong> — protects cellular health and promotes physiological balance</span>
